OL,6,FA woman has been charged following the
OL,7,Fdeath of a baby who was hit by a car
OL,8,Foutside Withybush General Hospital
OL,9,Flast year, police have confirmed.
OL,11,FBridget Carole Curtis, aged 70, of
OL,12,FBegelly, has been charged with causing
OL,13,Fthe death of eight-month-old Mabli
OL,14,FCariad Hall by driving dangerously on
OL,15,FJune 21, 2023.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Mabli's family said
OL,18,Fthat the past year had been "the most
OL,19,Fhorrendous time of our lives" and that
OL,20,F"every day is a day of pain" as they
OL,21,Fcome to terms with what happened.
