OL,6,FMs Curtis is set to appear at Llanelli
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on August 22.
OL,9,FThe full statement from Mabli's family
OL,10,Fis as follows: "As a family we wish to
OL,11,Fthank Dyfed-Powys Police for their
OL,12,Fdiligence and professionalism over the
OL,13,Flast year and for how they have
OL,14,Fexplained each step to us on our very
OL,15,Fdifficult journey. Their patience and
OL,16,Fsupport has been invaluable.
