OL,6,F"We are grateful that we have now
OL,7,Freached this stage of the process. We
OL,8,Funderstand we have more to come but
OL,9,Fthis is the biggest step forward we've
OL,10,Fhad since June last year.
OL,12,F"We want to thank our friends, family
OL,13,Fand well-wishers and who have
OL,14,Fsupported us throughout this
OL,15,Fchallenging time and will continue to
OL,16,Fsupport us as things progress. We will
OL,17,Fnever forget that love and support
OL,18,Fshown to us and for the memory of our
OL,19,Fprecious angel, Mabli Cariad."
